{
  "stem": "268.1",
  "chunk_idx": 3,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 5.1,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "But when he worked night shift, which means he had to go to work-- and sleep in the daytime, you know, and go to work, like, in the evening, he would leave home 5, 6-- 6 o'clock, and then I wouldn't see him, perhaps-- because in the morning when he got in, I went to school.",
      "word_count": 56
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "So I would only see him maybe a couple hours in the afternoon.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "He naturally would discuss my-- my homework, school, and ask me about my activities.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And we would talk some sports, and-- and probably the usual thing that a father and son [? are ?] doing, with the exception of limited time.",
      "word_count": 27
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Not so much leisure time, like long weekends, you know?",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "I must also add he worked, like, a six-day shift, so unfortunately, he had to work on Saturday, half a day.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "So those are my recollection about my father.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Summertime on vacation-- we would take vacations together.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Again, the coal miners had a wonderful benefit.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "They had what's called a sanatorium.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "It's a place where they would give, I think, something like four to six weeks, depending on one's health.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And the length of time he worked in the mines, he would get, like, a respite period in the mountains of Poland, mountains and also close to the forest, to the, like, pine forest where the air was supposedly cleaner and better for the lungs.",
      "word_count": 45
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "Because, you know, coal miners did suffer from lung diseases.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So that we would-- when he would be sent to this sanatorium, the whole family would-- would go along.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "We would rent a place, like, a couple rooms not far from him, and my dad would be in a sanatorium.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "We would meet for meals together, you know, we'll go out on the town.",
      "word_count": 14
    }
  ],
